WEBVTT

00:02:56.015 --> 00:03:00.507
and I hooked up with this super
cool guy; we talked a lot.

00:03:01.911 --> 00:03:04.904
Around 4am, I told my friends
it was time to go.

00:03:04.928 --> 00:03:06.703
They wanted to stay.

00:03:06.727 --> 00:03:09.626
So, the guy asked me where I lived

00:03:09.650 --> 00:03:12.477
and said if it was OK with me,
he'd drive me home.

00:03:12.501 --> 00:03:14.524
I agreed, and we left.

00:03:15.564 --> 00:03:19.685
At a stoplight, he told me
he liked me and touched my leg.

00:03:20.660 --> 00:03:23.320
I don't like a guy
to approach me that way,

00:03:23.344 --> 00:03:26.349
but he had been affectionate all night.

00:03:26.373 --> 00:03:29.214
I thought, 'I shouldn't be so paranoid.

00:03:29.238 --> 00:03:31.998
What if I say something but he
didn't mean anything by it,